<legis-body id="H13CA6937C31946FEAE134624F1455052" style="OLC"> 
<section id="H3187917717F94423A14142871C78211B" section-type="section-one"><enum>1.</enum><header>Short title</header><text display-inline="no-display-inline">This Act may be cited as the <quote><short-title>Federal Transit Modernization Act of 2015</short-title></quote>.</text></section> <section id="HE1601DCD197846D78D0EC04687F8F607"><enum>2.</enum><header>Employee protective arrangements</header> <subsection id="H791BAAE33FED475693A4BBF0ED87DA1A"><enum>(a)</enum><header>In general</header><text display-inline="yes-display-inline">Section 5333 of title 49, United States Code, is amended—</text> 
<paragraph id="HA68A803003084851BCAC03A72CCF8ECB"><enum>(1)</enum><text>by striking <quote>(a) <header-in-text level="subsection" style="USC">Prevailing wages requirement.—</header-in-text></quote>; and</text></paragraph> <paragraph id="H767D8F011DFF48FFBBEE72E7EE483886"><enum>(2)</enum><text>by striking subsection (b).</text></paragraph></subsection> 
<subsection id="HA17521B589D94B70B3EA0976F753CE7B"><enum>(b)</enum><header>Conforming amendments</header> 
<paragraph id="H48D03551E5DF41489ABC00D355B97BEE"><enum>(1)</enum><header>Formula grants for rural areas</header><text>Section 5311(i) of title 49, United States Code, is repealed.</text></paragraph> <paragraph id="H9A64998C1673480ABFB8611EFE0721F8"><enum>(2)</enum><header>Administrative provisions</header><text display-inline="yes-display-inline">Section 5334(a)(1) of title 49, United States Code, is amended by striking <quote>(except terms the Secretary of Labor prescribes under section 5333(b) of this title)</quote>.</text></paragraph></subsection></section> 
